msgid "A published release failed integrity verification"
msgstr "公開済みリリースの整合性検証に失敗しました"

#: includes/Admin/AdminSiteHealth.php:164
msgid ""
"Withdraw the affected release, isolate its package, and publish a newly "
"verified build."
msgstr ""
"対象リリースを停止してパッケージを隔離し、新しく検証したビルドを公開してくだ"
"さい。"

